# Summary
Microscope is an Amplitude feature that enables detailed exploration of chart data points, offering options like Zoom In, Filter By, Exclude, Create Cohort, View User Streams, Show User Paths, and Explore Conversion Drivers, allowing users to analyze individual user behaviors and create targeted guides or surveys.

